Artificial Intelligence

The Reward Engine will emit coins to users based on the contribution of users to 

the network. TomoCoin will also be used as a mean of payment for all services and 

third-party applications provided. Financial transaction will be hashed and stored in 

blockchain to ensure the security and transparency of the data and to maintain a high 

level of trust. TomoApp works with two chains: the first one is the Ethereum 

blockchain which will be used to issue ERC-20 token and allow users to sell and buy 

tokens via third party exchanges. The second is a side chain (TomoChain) that will host 

all financial transaction within TomoApp. Both the sidechain and the Reward engine 

will interact via our Smart Contracts. 

Blockchain and Smart Contract 

TomoWallet; ii) Social Services: This tree serves social functionalities such as 

