Tomo application; fourthly, TomoCoin being used as the native payment method 

within Tomo application and other third-party services.  

We have a long-term commitment to complete the product, engineering and 

marketing roadmap for the Tomo network including Tomo application, TomoChain and 

TomoWallet. Consequently, figuring out the resources needed to get the works done 

effectively, we estimate to spend at least one and half million $ per year over 4 year 

